| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1494 — Recovery Inhibition (nokoyawa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0b80fb63-15fe-5cfd-b68d-cb6cc61d5a4a"
